            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Solo owners on a tight budget who already write their own posts.</div>
            <a href="https://buffer.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">03</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Hootsuite</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Multi-platform veteran</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$99<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Professional plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Broadest integration set on the market</li>
                <li>Strong streams + monitoring view</li>
                <li>Team and approval workflows</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Pricing climbs steeply with seats and profiles</li>
                <li>Feature density is overwhelming for solo owners</li>
