            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Per-seat pricing makes it brutal at multi-user scale</li>
                <li>Overpowered for a single-location operator</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Multi-location chains and franchise marketing teams.</div>
            <a href="https://sproutsocial.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
